700685f-b.title: Bronx: Bryant Avenue - Boston Road
700685f-b.text:
(1)
Bryant Avenue, east side, north from but not including
Boston Road, to and including E. Tremont Avenue. The square
2-story brick house bears No. 1932 and the 2 -story frame house
adjoining the apartment house bears No. 1942. The 6-story
apartment house at the S.E. corner of E. Tremont Ave. bears
No. 1004 on the latter.
July 31, 1928
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(2)
Part of the same, showing a closer view of No. 1942 Bryant
AVenue and 1004 E. Tremont Avenue.
July 31, 1928
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
